{"tid":1252991,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以後你唔搵我","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:22:38.000Z","uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c99c8e795b1823063e1531417db297c95e9d82c","tid":1252991,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"我唔會搵你 怕你又覺得我俾壓力你<br />\n<br />\n你搵我 我會推<br />\n我怕你為左怕我自殺所以先分時間俾我<br />\n<br />\n你放心 我唔會自殺<br />\n你知我好細膽 我只會每日祈求我可以早啲死<br />\n等你依一世都會記得我"},{"pid":"c08d4267e7e4358c0b8ceecf99673a2502653e58","tid":1252991,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"原來我咁天真<br />\n我咩都同你分享 覺得你會好想知 <br />\n我覺得同你分享好開心<br />\n但原來你根本覺得每日只係需要一兩個message維繫感情<br />\n我多餘 我想你每日打一兩個電話俾我 我想你聽我電話 我想你話我知你做梗咩 我想見你<br />\n全部都係我多餘 我要求多 我要求越黎越多<br />\n我俾太多壓力你 <br />\n我以後唔會再俾壓力你"},{"pid":"5bf419c454ce791394de9cad2dd5f3cf48f2b6ad","tid":1252991,"uid":258484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"哈 以後真係冇人再俾到壓力你了<br />\n因為你決定唔要我了"},{"pid":"f2321745a10bc98d25bb38f952c4172c97bc8a5e","tid":1252991,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"善"},{"pid":"2fbc57d9b75da0c58e448d9a4eb2379e3a754bad","tid":1252991,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"學識獨立<br />\n就唔怕寂莫"},{"pid":"024e54e5a3c11c8b955693372a6295c9cea580c0","tid":1252991,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"我心聲黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36fd761e7c05a3a53b396fa14c669e07e2dd4c4","tid":1252991,"uid":152695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"一睇字就知你係恐怖情人啦 郁下又用自殺黎情緒勒索人"},{"pid":"9450eca21e26a11c41ea682af3956e1bca341861","tid":1252991,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f36fd761e7c05a3a53b396fa1